---
title: Beef and Mushroom Spaghetti with Balsamic-Glazed Tomatoes
description: This dish is a perfect balance of savoury and sweet! Beef and mushrooms make a rich, umami ragu, while bursting baby tomatoes and balsamic glaze add a bright pop of tangy sweetness!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spaghettis-au-boeuf-et-aux-champignons-5d9925c9.jpg
